               <msContents>
                  <summary>Miracles of Jesus, ተአምረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="4r" to="64r" facs="006">Fols 4r–64r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Eighteen Miracles of Jesus, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተአምረ፡ ኢየሱስ፡</foreign></note>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="4r" to="16v" facs="006">Fols 4r–16v</locus><title>Biblical Readings for Horologium for the Night Hours</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="18r" to="31r" facs="020">Fols 18r–31r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Introduction: Miracle of Jesus: How he tells John, the son of Zebedee, about his coming. <locus target="#26" facs="028">Fol. 26</locus> is dislocated</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="31r" to="33r" facs="033">Fols 31r–33r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: The Nativity of Our Lord</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="33r" to="39r" facs="035">Fols 33r–39r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: The Baptism and temptation of Jesus</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from="39v" to="43r" facs="042">Fols 39v–43r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: About Palm Sunday</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6"><locus from="43r" to="45r" facs="045">Fols 43r–45r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: The Last Supper, the washing of the feet and the arrest of Jesus. Though the quire is intact, there is a lacuna in the text between folios <locus target="#43v #44r" facs="046">folss. 43v, 44r, </locus>. <locus target="#26r #26v" facs="028 029">26r, 26v</locus> contains some of the missing text, though it does not match perfectly</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7"><locus from="45r" to="47r" facs="047">Fols 45r–47r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: The Passion of Jesus and the Conversation with the Thief on the Cross</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.8"><locus from="47r" to="48r" facs="049">Fols 47r–48r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: About Holy Saturday Morning, the end of Judas Iscariot</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.9"><locus from="48r" to="52v" facs="050">Fols 48r–52v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: About His Resurrection</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10"><locus from="52v" to="54v" facs="055">Fols 52v–54v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: About His Ascension</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11"><locus from="54v" to="57r" facs="057">Fols 54v–57r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: About the Descent of the Holy Spirit on the Day of Pentecost</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12"><locus from="57r" to="57v" facs="059">Fols 57r–57v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: How he learned all the biblical books in seven days, how he mixed and separated the ink of his teacher</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.13"><locus from="57v" to="58v" facs="059">Fols 57v–58v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: How he travelled on rays of light with his childhood friends</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.14"><locus from="58v" to="59v" facs="061">Fols 58v–59v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: How he made birds from the mud</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.15"><locus from="59v" to="61r" facs="062">Fols 59v–61r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: Salome praises Our Lord</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.16"><locus from="61r" to="61v" facs="063">Fols 61r–61v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: How Jesus went to Jerusalem with his disciples</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.17"><locus from="61v" to="65v" facs="064">Fols 61v–65v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2382Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  ʾIyasus</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Miracle of Jesus: How Jesus Wept over Jerusalem</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.18"><locus from="65v" to="67r" facs="068">Fols 65v–67r</locus><title>Presentation of the Child Jesus to the Temple</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                </msItem>
